            <p>Dear {!X1Y_Satisfaction_Survey_Result__c.Contact__c},</p>
            <p>Our records indicate that you’ve had a SunPower solar system producing energy for your home for more than a year. We want to hear how it’s going, and hope you can take this <a href="http://survey.sunpowercorp.com/go?iv=244tebwf4rw6y&q1={!X1Y_Satisfaction_Survey_Result__c.Lease__c}&q2={!X1Y_Satisfaction_Survey_Result__c.Opportunity__c}&q3={!X1Y_Satisfaction_Survey_Result__c.OpportunityId__c}&q4={!X1Y_Satisfaction_Survey_Result__c.Id}">survey</a> to let us know! <br>
            </p>
            <p>We recognize the importance of an ongoing dialog with our customers. Your feedback will help us continue to refine our products and services with the goal of providing you the best customer experience and the highest energy production from your system.<br><br>
Please take this survey covering the time since your solar system first began producing energy by clicking the link: <a href="http://survey.sunpowercorp.com/go?iv=244tebwf4rw6y&q1={!X1Y_Satisfaction_Survey_Result__c.Lease__c}&q2={!X1Y_Satisfaction_Survey_Result__c.Opportunity__c}&q3={!X1Y_Satisfaction_Survey_Result__c.OpportunityId__c}&q4={!X1Y_Satisfaction_Survey_Result__c.Id}">SunPower Customer Survey</a>. Depending on your answers it will take about 10 minutes to complete.<br>
 </p>
            <p>If you have questions or need immediate assistance, please contact our Customer Care team directly at 1(800)SUNPOWER or by email at <a href=mailto:customercare@sunpowercorp.com>CustomerCare@sunpowercorp.com</a>.</p>
            <p>Thank you for choosing SunPower.<br><br><br> </p>
